data.title: Bellringing at All Saints Church, Worcester
data.text:
Notes

Located on the North side of the junction of Quay St and Bridge St. Worcester shopping centre is close by and has many quality shops too. There is a pleasant walk along nearby River Severn. The County cricket ground and racecourse all within a short distance.

On practice nights if the access door is locked please call 0 7 5 0 1 1 8 3 3 3 1
